precis:
Amendment to the CF-18 HORNET AIRCRAFT REMISSION ORDER which will extend
the period over the course of which a remission of customs duties and sales
tax will be granted on goods imported for the manufacture, maintenance and
testing of CF-18 aircraft, until August 31, 1992.
